div.div: Vertices are now packed and hopefully somewhat future proof
Geometry editor now can highlight and isolate different sub meshes
Logger console (sometimes) scrolls to bottom automatically
Fbx importer can handle different file structures better now
Fixed incorrect signs calculation causing inversed normal z values
Created a geometry viewer to view imported models and meshes
Implemented FBX importing into the editor and enabled drag/drop for the asset browser
Refactored some typing and enum conventions
